Class NBATeamSelect

  • java.lang.Object
    • NBATeam
      • NBATeamSelect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenStats

    public class NBATeamSelect
extends NBATeam
implements GenStats
    This class inherits from NBATeam and implements GenStats. By including an NBATeam object in its constructor, the information is passed into the TeamSelectObject, this is where the random statistics will be generated without effecting the original NBATeam object.
